quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,164,"Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀, ìtẹ̀léǹtẹ̀lé òru àti ọ̀sán, àti àwọn ọkọ̀ ojú-omi tó ń rìn lórí omi pẹ̀lú (ríru) ohun tó ń ṣe àwọn ènìyàn ní àǹfààní, àti ohun tí Allāhu ń sọ̀kalẹ̀ ní omi láti sánmọ̀, tí Ó sì ń fi sọ ilẹ̀ di ààyè lẹ́yìn tí ó ti kú, àti (bí) Ó ṣe fọ́n gbogbo ẹranko ká sí orí ilẹ̀, àti ìyípadà atẹ́gùn<sup>1</sup> àti ẹ̀ṣújò tí A tẹ̀ba láààrin sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀; (àmì wà nínú wọn) fún ìjọ tó ń ṣe làákàyè.","[1] Ìyípadà atẹ́gùn túmọ̀ sí oríṣi atẹ́gùn àti àwọn ibùfẹ́ atẹ́gùn."
  2,165,"Ó sì ń bẹ nínú àwọn ènìyàn, ẹni tí ó ń jọ́sìn fún àwọn òrìṣà lẹ́yìn Allāhu. Wọ́n nífẹ̀ẹ́ wọn gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìfẹ́ (tó yẹ kí wọ́n ní sí) Allāhu. Àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo sì le jùlọ nínú ìfẹ́ sí Allāhu. Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé àwọn tó ṣàbòsí lè rí ìgbà tí wọ́n máa rí Ìyà náà ni, (wọn ìbá mọ̀ pé) dájúdájú gbogbo agbára ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu. Àti pé dájúdájú Allāhu le (níbi) ìyà.",""
  2,166,"(Rántí) nígbà tí àwọn tí wọ́n tẹ̀lé (ìyẹn àwọn aṣíwájú kèfèrí) bá yọwọ́ yọsẹ̀ kúrò nínú ọ̀rọ̀ àwọn tó tẹ̀lé wọn; (nígbà tí) wọ́n bá fojú rí Ìyà, tí ohun tó so wọ́n pọ̀ sì já pátápátá.",""
  2,167,"Àwọn tó tẹ̀lé wọn yó sì wí pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé dájúdájú ìpadàwáyé lè wà fún wa ni, àwa ìbá yọwọ́ yọsẹ̀ kúrò nínú ọ̀rọ̀ wọn gẹ́gẹ́ bí wọ́n ṣe yọwọ́ yọsẹ̀ kúrò nínú ọ̀rọ̀ wa.” Báyẹn ni Allāhu yó ṣe fi àwọn iṣẹ́ wọn hàn wọ́n ní (iṣẹ́) òfò fún wọn. Wọn kò sì níí jáde kúrò nínú Iná.",""
  2,168,"Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn, ẹ jẹ nínú ohun tí ń bẹ nínú ilẹ̀ (tó jẹ́) ẹ̀tọ́ (àti n̄ǹkan) dáadáa. Ẹ má sì ṣe tẹ̀lé àwọn ojú-ẹsẹ̀ aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n. Dájúdájú òun ni ọ̀tá pọ́nńbélé fún yín.",""
  2,169,"Ohun tí ó máa pa yín ní àṣẹ rẹ̀ ni (iṣẹ́) aburú, ìbàjẹ́ àti pé kí ẹ máa pa irọ́ ohun tí ẹ kò nímọ̀ nípa rẹ̀ mọ́ Allāhu.",""
